title: Tour Customs: Wedge Stamps
headline: Tour Customs: Wedge Stamps
description: Club stamping started as a means for clubmakers to avoid confusion, but it's since evolved into a source of personal pride for Tour pros. From initials to movie quotes, here’s some of our favorite wedge stamps.
